description: Year of the Loong 🐲🐉 🔴🟡🟢 Author Fang Yuan, Artist 👩🏻‍🎨🎨 known as FAYA, is a post-90s artist who independently completed a 10k NFT project on the Ethereum blockchain from 2021 to 2022. Her artworks have been exhibited in various locations, including Germany and Italy. Yi Loong, a group of Loongs from (the I Ching,The Art of Change) has been dormant in Chinese mythology and is set to awaken in the Year of the Loong, 2024. It represents a mysterious force from the East, and the Loongs Gate endures!
name: Year of the Loong 🐲🐉 🔴🟡🟢
